long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: The Chrome extension reads the requests made by the browser, displays the requests, and allows you to view the body of the responses. You can select the requests you want and then add them to a project in app.mockfly.dev. This extension is a useful tool for developers to monitor and manage HTTP requests while they work on their projects.
